306
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, vraćam se sad u moj tadašnji život.

307
00:32:30,700 --> 00:32:35,680
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bio sam pametan, želio sam biti normalni krščni.

308
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta to znači.

309
00:32:36,819 --> 00:32:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne previše, nemoj previše uzbuđivati druge ljudi.

310
00:32:41,599 --> 00:32:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] Budi normalan, jer sam sada džakom.

311
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam džakom, moram biti normalan.

312
00:32:46,799 --> 00:32:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali živio sam dvostruki život na neki način.

313
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećate se kralja Davida?

314
00:32:55,559 --> 00:32:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je kralj, imao je pomazanje, bio je izabran.

315
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] A onda je poželio jednu ženu od jednog vojnika

316
00:33:03,039 --> 00:33:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] i bio je spreman napraviti greh i dati ga ubiti, da su ga ubili.

317
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] I tako sam se ja osjećao.

318
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:21,339
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, 12. mjesec, prosinac, bio je vrijeme velike zabave.

319
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tada smo imali novogodišnje odkupljenja, hrane, piče,

320
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] oni direktori tu, direktori tamo, restorani tamo.

321
00:33:31,099 --> 00:33:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] I ponašao sam se kao direktor, kao menedžer,

322
00:33:34,859 --> 00:33:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] a ne kao krščanin, a manje kao džakom.

323
00:33:38,740 --> 00:33:43,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nisam počinjao nikakve velike grijehe,

324
00:33:44,559 --> 00:33:46,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali bil sam konformist.

325
00:33:46,359 --> 00:33:48,140
[SPEAKER_00] I šta sam osjećao?

326
00:33:48,140 --> 00:33:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] Izgubil sam snagu duha svetoga.

327
00:33:50,799 --> 00:33:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, i znao sam, da to nije pravi put,

328
00:33:56,119 --> 00:33:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam nastavio.

329
00:33:57,700 --> 00:34:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svi so me hvalili, imel sam odličan status,

330
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] uspjeh, napredoval sam.

331
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju sam bio ravnatelj jednog staračkog doma

332
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] za starije osobe sa 130 zaposlenika

333
00:34:12,579 --> 00:34:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] i 230 stareh ljudi.

334
00:34:14,619 --> 00:34:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] Velika institucija.

335
00:34:16,059 --> 00:34:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] I tada se nam rodio četvrti sin, Jonatan.

336
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna gospođa je htjela dati,

337
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:28,280
[SPEAKER_00] i tražili smo neki novi smještaj stan,

338
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] in neka gospođa je htjela dati kučo preko župnika.

339
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo to prihvatili kao neko veliko čudo,

340
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] i mi smo jo običali, da ćemo se briniti za nju.

341
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, napravili smo ugovor.

342
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] I prvi put smo se sreli s tom gospođom

343
00:34:48,579 --> 00:34:50,619
