344
00:34:50,619 --> 00:34:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] I zatim nakon pola godine smo se uselili to kuču.

345
00:34:55,579 --> 00:34:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] Uzeli smo velike kredite, jer smo imali dobre plače,

346
00:34:59,639 --> 00:35:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] jel tako, in nakon godine dana počeli so prvi problemi.

347
00:35:05,579 --> 00:35:08,739
