348
00:35:08,739 --> 00:35:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] da jih damo ključe in da zaboravimo sve.

349
00:35:10,679 --> 00:35:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] A mi smo imali velike kredite in tako.

350
00:35:13,119 --> 00:35:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nismo mi odmah odustali, ona je dala tužbe na sud,

351
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:27,019
