391
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvata.

392
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] On že, on zna zašto.

393
00:38:21,059 --> 00:38:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali onda neki dan mi je rekao,

394
00:38:24,119 --> 00:38:25,340
