395
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad sem mu to sve ispričal

396
00:38:27,159 --> 00:38:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] in tako, kaže Matej,

397
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] jer ti želiš živeti

398
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:33,539
