401
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo čudo, što se dogodilo,

402
00:38:40,679 --> 00:38:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] je, kad sem bil na Polskoj.

403
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kad sem več izgubil status,

404
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] kad sem izgubil posao,

405
